fields.name: Defending the Kingdom
fields.description: Clash for crown and glory, repel invasions, lead incursions, bring victory to the land and people.

fields.name: Calm
fields.description: Perfect stillness and serenity.

fields.name: Gothic Storm
fields.description: Ancient voices whisper under the roll of thunderous storms. Find what lurks in the towers and the lowlands.

fields.name: First Contact
fields.description: Mysterious lights, strange shapes, figures in the mist. You are their first encounter. Do they bring peace or terror?

fields.name: Twilight of Magick
fields.description: Within the barrier between night and day lies the last vestiges of an ancient order of powerful sorcerers. You are among them.

fields.name: Serene Jouney
fields.description: Float lightly across sleeping scenery and lush landscapes. Dense forests, majestic mountains and babbling brooks.

fields.name: Adventure
fields.description: Pure adrenaline infused with challenge and high notes of action.

fields.name: Fear
fields.description: Spine tingling certainty of doom.

fields.name: Headgear 1000
fields.description: Aisling Dreamshop’s most advanced headgear model. The HD1000, offers next-gen REM PROJECTION with simultaneous multi-sensory I/O mindfeed.

fields.name: Dream Mixer
fields.description: Select your own blend of Ingredients and mix customised experiences to dream, share or gift.

fields.name: HD ReREM Dream Device
fields.description: Record, Share and Re-dream in full HD quality.

fields.name: Hope
fields.description: The promise of better and a positive outlook.

fields.name: Victory
fields.description: Unquestioned achievement and the fire of glory.

fields.name: Nothingness
fields.description: A complete lack of sensory activity.

fields.name: Romance
fields.description: Passion with hues of love.

fields.name: Acceptance
fields.description: A steadfast foundation of understanding and approval.

fields.name: Ethereal
fields.description: Shapeless, formless but evident.

fields.name: Surprise
fields.description: Apparent normality until it isn’t.

fields.name: Companionship
fields.description: The warmth of togetherness and belonging.

fields.name: No Control
fields.description: Absolute lack of self determination or control.

fields.name: New Stardom
fields.description: This is the moment, the stars have aligned and you have achieved greatness. Bask in the adoration and attention.

fields.name: True Flight
fields.description: Soar to great heights, effortless and with full control. Witness the edges of space, zoom the skies, glide over waterways and plains.

fields.name: The Edge
fields.description: What awaits you in the stillness, just beyond the edge of your view. Move towards the edge and discover its truths.

fields.name: Synthesis
fields.description: In the world of the microcosm even the smallest activity takes on epic proportions. Transform into adventure.

fields.name: Hunted
fields.description: The snap of a twig, cold air fills your lungs, you feel the atmosphere change. You are hunted.

fields.name: The Maze
fields.description: Paths cut through shapes, sheer walls of smooth stone, each turn brings the hope of escape. Can you leave the maze?

fields.name: Zen Beach
fields.description: On an oasis of cool sand, calm waters and smooth stones you will find stillness and restful peace.

fields.name: Cosmic Swirl
fields.description: You are at the nucleus of a pulsating cosmos of light and energy, a synergy of sound and matter. Travel through time and space.

fields.name: Bubbles
fields.description: Float in a weightless world, bobbing and weaving through cool waters and endless streams.

fields.name: Crash Landing
fields.description: The mundane hum of another uneventful journey is suddenly snapped and disaster now looms below. Can you find a way out and survive?

fields.name: Stationary Orbit
fields.description: Among the pings and hums of space life spectacles await at every turn. What lies just over the crest of the next orbit?

fields.name: Shareware Hub
fields.description: The Aisling Shareware Hub allows users to connect up to 6 Headgears to one HD Replay Device. Chain Shareware Hubs to expand further.
